<p style=3D'margin-top:6pt;margin-bottom:6pt;font-family:PMingLiU;font-size=
:11.0pt;
color:black'>不孕症（Infertility）指的是夫妻在無避孕的情況=
下，經過<span style=3D'font-weight:bold'>一年</span>（女性年齡=
35歲則為<span
style=3D'font-weight:bold'>六個月</span>）的規律性生活仍無法=
孕。</p>

